import { FaBars } from "react-icons/fa";

function Navbar() {
    return ( <
        header >
        <
        nav >
        <
        a href = "/#" > notifications < /a> <
        a href = "/#" > Home < /a> <
        a href = "/#" > Home < /a>

        <
        /nav>  <
        button >
        <
        FaBars / >
        <
        /button>

        <
        /header >
    );
}

export default Navbar;
